《'''吸血鬼紀事'''》，又稱《'''吸血鬼年鑑'''》或《'''吸血鬼歷代紀'''》（英語：{{lang|en|The Vampire Chronicles}}）是美國作家[[安·萊絲|安·萊絲]]所著的一系列[[吸血鬼|吸血鬼]]小說的總稱，小說故事始於並圍繞着一名虛構的18世紀法國貴族{{tsl|en|Lestat de Lioncourt|黎斯特·德·萊昂柯特}}轉化為吸血鬼之後展開。此套系列小說敍事的時空背景也以18世紀末的[[紐奧良|紐奧良]]為原點，再上下挪移，縱跨[[世紀末|世紀末]]巴黎的衣香鬢影、[[法國大革命|法國大革命]]時期的失序世界、[[中世紀|中世紀]]的陰沈動盪、[[古羅馬|古羅馬]]的狂歡饗宴，直逼[[古埃及|古埃及]]王朝的殘酷壯麗全景，編織出一幅上至遠古，下達20世紀末的群魔繡帷；而吸血族版圖也自歐洲橫跨至美洲新大陸，展現超自然世界的慾望、絕望與狂夢。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ireader.cc/index.php/study/study_01_5_detail?sn=178532&article_sn=374091|title=正宗吸血鬼女王安萊絲最華麗的饗宴}}{{Dead link|date=2019年5月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }} iReader</ref>

萊絲在2008年的一次採訪中說她筆下的吸血鬼是「迷失靈魂的隱喩」，<ref name="Time 2008">{{cite web |url=http://www.time.com/time/video/player/0,32068,1446813083_1722024,00.html |title=10 Questions for Anne Rice |work=[[Time_(magazine)|Time]] |first=Carolyn |last=Sayre |year=2008 |accessdate=November 4, 2014 |archive-date=2013-08-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130826155422/http://www.time.com/time/video/player/0,32068,1446813083_1722024,00.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref>而《吸血鬼紀事》裡隱含的{{tsl|en|Homoeroticism|同性戀情色|同性情色}}傾向也是有豐富的文獻紀錄。<ref name="Keller 12-14">{{cite book |title=Anne Rice and Sexual Politics: The Early Novels |first=James R. |last=Keller |publisher=McFarland |year=2000 |isbn=978-0786408467 |pages=12–14 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=zM7tFSNAiXUC&pg=PA12&lpg=PA12&dq=anne+rice+homoerotic&source=bl&ots=k9VRYiPkaE&sig=AQ3OhOeV7ldxjBYVwVt1cnM8Cpg&hl=en&sa=X&ei=iDyrU_A_jIaiBPCigsAK&ved=0CDkQ6AEwAjgK#v=onepage&q=anne%20rice%20homoerotic&f=false |access-date=2017-03-11 |archive-date=2017-02-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170222110525/https://books.google.com/books?id=zM7tFSNAiXUC&pg=PA12&lpg=PA12&dq=anne+rice+homoerotic&source=bl&ots=k9VRYiPkaE&sig=AQ3OhOeV7ldxjBYVwVt1cnM8Cpg&hl=en&sa=X&ei=iDyrU_A_jIaiBPCigsAK&ved=0CDkQ6AEwAjgK#v=onepage&q=anne%20rice%20homoerotic&f=false |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Salon 1996">{{cite web |url=http://www.salon.com/1996/09/16/questions_5/ |title=Submit to Anne |website=Salon.com |date=September 16, 1996 |accessdate=June 25, 2014 |archive-date=2020-11-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201125001054/https://www.salon.com/1996/09/16/questions_5/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="NYT Maslin 1994">{{cite news |url=https://www.nytimes.com/1994/11/11/movies/film-review-interview-with-the-vampire-rapture-and-terror-bound-by-blood.html? |title=Film Review: ''Interview with the Vampire''; Rapture and Terror, Bound by Blood |first=Janet |last=Maslin |date=November 11, 1994 |work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]] |accessdate=June 25, 2014 |archive-date=2020-09-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200922100319/https://www.nytimes.com/1994/11/11/movies/film-review-interview-with-the-vampire-rapture-and-terror-bound-by-blood.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="NYT James 1994">{{cite news |url=https://www.nytimes.com/1994/11/13/movies/in-search-of-the-man-within-the-monster.html? |title=In Search of the Man Within the Monster |first=Caryn |last=James |date=November 13, 1994 |work=The New York Times |accessdate=June 25, 2014 |archive-date=2019-12-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191225124112/https://www.nytimes.com/1994/11/13/movies/in-search-of-the-man-within-the-monster.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>截止到2008年11月，此系列小說在世界範圍內售出8千萬冊。<ref name="Telegraph 2008-11">{{cite web |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/donotmigrate/3562792/Anne-Rice-interview-with-the-vampire-writer.html |title=Anne Rice: interview with the vampire writer |work=[[The_Daily_Telegraph|The Telegraph]] |first=Stuart |last=Husband |date=November 2, 2008 |accessdate=August 10, 2014 |archive-date=2017-12-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171213042527/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/donotmigrate/3562792/Anne-Rice-interview-with-the-vampire-writer.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

《吸血鬼紀事》系列的第一部《[[夜訪吸血鬼_(小說)|夜訪吸血鬼]]》於1994年被改編成[[夜訪吸血鬼|同名電影]]，由[[湯姆·克魯斯|湯姆·克魯斯]]、[[布萊德·彼特|布萊德·彼特]]、[[安東尼奧·班德拉斯|安東尼奧·班德拉斯]]、[[克利斯汀·史萊特|克利斯汀·史萊特]]和[[克絲汀·鄧斯特|克絲汀·鄧斯特]]等主演。第三部《[[天譴者的女王|天譴者的女王]]》於2002年改編為電影《[[屍纏妖后|-{zh-tw:魔咒女王; zh-hk:屍纏妖后; zh-cn:吸血鬼女王}-]]》，由[[艾莉亞|艾莉亞]]、[[史都華·唐森|史都華·唐森]]和[[文森·培瑞茲|文森·培瑞茲]]等主演，此片加入了部份來自第二部小說《[[吸血鬼黎斯特|吸血鬼黎斯特]]》的情節。2014年8月，[[環球影業|環球影業]]和 [[Imagine_Entertainment|Imagine Entertainment]] 收購了全系列小說的影視版權。<ref name="Variety 2014-08">{{cite web |url=http://variety.com/2014/film/news/anne-rices-vampire-chronicles-takes-flight-at-universal-1201278069/ |title=Anne Rice's ''Vampire Chronicles'' Takes Flight at Universal |first=Dave |last=McNary |work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] |date=August 7, 2014 |accessdate=August 10, 2014 |archive-date=2020-11-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111171740/https://variety.com/2014/film/news/anne-rices-vampire-chronicles-takes-flight-at-universal-1201278069/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>2016年11月，萊絲在[[臉書|臉書]]公佈自己著作的戲院版權回歸她手中。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dramaqueen.com.tw/news/20161128/004.html|title=《夜訪吸血鬼》系列小說有望拍攝電視影集}} DramaQueen電視迷</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.ew.com/article/2016/11/26/anne-rice-plotting-vampire-chronicles-tv-series-adaptation|title=Anne Rice Plotting 'The Vampire Chronicles' TV Series Adaptation|newspaper=Entertainment Weekly's EW.com|access-date=2016-11-28|archive-date=2016-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161129111912/http://www.ew.com/article/2016/11/26/anne-rice-plotting-vampire-chronicles-tv-series-adaptation|dead-url=no}}</ref>

